 with the ability to travel nearly anywhere in Norrath on a whim, Druids are the best casual player soloist in the game bar none.</P><P>Frankly, Druids have so many advantages as a solo class they really should be PUNISHED in the end game, as Necromancers currently are.  </P><P>If you doubt me do a “/who all druid 60” and a “/who all necromancer 60” and compare the results.  Keeping in mind the vast majority of Druids go anonymous.  </P><P>Druids whining for enhancements is a frigging joke on a monumental scale. </P><P><BR><img src="http://www.gibnet.gi/~rondu/necromancer.jpg" border=0></font></td>
